A religious socio-political Evangelist and businessman, Apostle Chris Omashola, has revealed what God told him about Nigerian singer, Naira Marley. As part of his prophecies for the year 2020, the evangelist said God told him that rave of the moment, Naira Marley is a demon and Satanic and must repent before it is too late. He said God told him that Naira Marley’s songs are demonically inspired to destroy the destiny of Nigerian youths. ”In 2020, God told me, Naira Marley is A Demon, He is Satanic and should repent before it’s too late. “His songs are demonically inspired to destroy the Destiny of The Youths of this generation, Nigerian youths should desist from calling themselves Marlians” he wrote via Twitter. 10. In 2020, God told me, Naira Marley is A Demon, He is Satanic and should repent before it’s too late. His songs are demonically inspired to destroy the Destiny of The Youths of this generation, Nigerian youths should desist from calling themselves Marlians. #ACOProphecies2020 pic.twitter.com/Bzv2tWxbGx — Apostle Chris Omashola (@chrisomashola) January 7, 2020 